@NODE "Intro" "Introduction"

@{B}@{U}@{JCENTER}Introduction@{UB}@{UU}

@{JLEFT}
Matchball is a Tennis game Martin started to write as it seems that there will
be no alternative to Great Courts 2. He tries to program it as modular as
possible, so that its easy to change various parts of the game. This project
is in early stage and still beta. So try it on your own risk.


@{B}@{U}@{JCENTER}Already Implemented Parts@{UB}@{UU}
Over 200 Animation Frames
128 Colors
Top-Spin, Drive, Slice, Lob (all Forehand and Backhand), Smash, Service.
AHI-SFX
Adverts
Different Grandstands
Training


