@NODE "Req" "Requirements"


All you @{"should" LINK "Help"} need to play the demo:


lowlevel.library

AHI V4.0

AGA *

68020 or higher **

Helvetica.font (If you don't have this Font you have to edit the Data/Advert.inf File)

OS 3.1 (3.0) ***

Harddisk  (~1 MB free space)

CD32 - PAD





* As this game uses only OS calls it could be possible to play it with
  Graphic-Cards Emulation. As we don't have a Gfx-Card I have no clue
  about this ...

** We tried it with an 030/50 MHz. I don't think that a 020 is fast
   enough.

*** A OS 3.0 with the newest SetPatch should be enough.




We tested the game on an Amiga 1200 with this system-configuration:


68030 / 50 MHz

64 MB (not necessary for this demo)

AGA

OS 3.1




